title: Cubanos
content:
Cubanos is a classical must make sandwitch. 

Ingredients:

  • Pork 
  • Sauce
  • Yellow mustard
  • Dill pickles

Making instructions:

  1. Make marinade and marinade the meat at least overnight
  2. Make bread
  3. Slow cook the meat for 3 hours
  4. Assemble cubano: toast bread, put mustard, pickles, meat, cheese
  5. Toast cubano in a pan
